<main>
    <div class="info">
        <section>
            <h2>Who Josh is...</h2>
            <p>He is a <em>computer science student</em> at Oregon State University. Currently
                he works as a <em>Program Coordinator</em> at Seattle Children's Hospital, helping
            to develop their new apheresis department.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>What Josh is about...</h2>
            <p>He is all about <em>hard work</em>, <em>discpline</em>, and <em>minimalism</em>. He enjoys reading
            books, exploring ideas, and trialing new ways to improve himself. He has
            a dream of everything he owns fitting into his vehicle.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>What Josh likes to do...</h2>
            <p>He likes to make things. He enjoys writing <em>Python</em>, tolerates writing
                <em>JavaScript</em>, and absolutely adores writing <em>assembly</em>. When he's not writing
            code, he can likely be found taking long walks throughout the city in which
            he lives or a nearby park.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>Fiction I've been reading:</h2>
        <span>(All images from <a href="http://openlibrary.org/" target="_blank">
            http://openlibrary.org/</a>)</span>
        <div class="carousel_container">
            <div class="carousel_arrow">
                <img src="images/left.png" alt="Left Arrow" id="left_arrow">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel">
                {{#if books}}
                    {{#each books}}
                        <section class="books">
                            <a href="{{this.url}}" target="_blank">
                                <img src="{{this.cover}}" alt="{{this.bookTitle}} cover">
                                <div>
                                    <h3>{{this.bookTitle}}</h3>
                                    <p>{{this.author}}</p>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </section>
                    {{/each}}
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            <div class="carousel_arrow">
                <img src="images/right.png" alt="Right Arrow" id="right_arrow">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
